886
01:15:47,820 --> 01:15:48,820
Mau đi chuẩn bị đi.

887
01:16:09,170 --> 01:16:12,910
[Mạch]

888
01:17:55,750 --> 01:17:56,200
Hay!

889
01:17:56,290 --> 01:17:57,670
Hay! Hay lắm!

890
01:18:05,960 --> 01:18:06,820
Nhiếp Linh Nhi,

891
01:18:07,880 --> 01:18:10,010
